snippet.title: Lana Comments on Your Comments 2

localized.description:
EWETOOB! Welcome to my channel, where every Thursday I do everything from comedy sketches to songs, vlogs, cartoons, and collaborations with sexy people.

My name is Lana McKissack, and if you are a NigaHiga fan, you may recognize me from the YOMYOMF channel's "Internet Icon."  Since I have a million different interests and have trouble making up my mind, you can think of my channel as one big variety show where my main goal is to show you a good time! Sometimes I do movie parodies, other days I do song covers with my many talented YouTube friends, sometimes I play "Lana Libs" with awesome people like Wong Fu Productions and Chester See, and sometimes I vlog or comment on your comments. You never know what you're gonna get. But I guarantee that at least I'LL be having a good time. And I hope you do too.

Be sure to SUBSCRIBE for a new video every Thursday because my mom says I'm a funny girl. Or she might've said funny looking. My Japanese is rusty.

http://clicktotweet.com/gMn02

If you missed the original video, here is the link:
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lMSRheVVK7I&feature=relmfu

The man behind the camera and in front of the editing bay, 

Nathan Moore: http://www.imdb.com/name/nm1994245/

Check out my store and buy an awesome McKickass shirt.
http://lanamckissack.spreadshirt.com/

I can also be found at:
http://www.twitter.com/lanamckissack
http://www.facebook.com/lanamckissackofficial
http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0572001/
http://www.irishninjacomedy.com

Thank ewe guys and gals for continuing to send me happy tweets and comments.  It really does make my day!

snippet.title: Can't Resist (Original)

localized.description:
CHORUS:
How can I resist you boy?
All I know is that when you're around, I wanna be close to you.
Feelings come and feelings go,
But I can't pretend that I don't see the look in your eyes whenever I pass by.

I think you understand how I feel for you when you are near.
(Oh baby, come on)
Ooh, all night I stay awake because I'm missing you.
You are in all my dreams.

I want you boy (oh baby, come on)
You want me too.
Take me in your arms.

REPEAT CHORUS

Now, I know this can't be love.
I'm just craving you, want you with me.
(Oh baby, come on)
'Cause you fill me with excitement when you're kissing me.
Put me in ecstasy.

I want you boy (oh baby, come on)
You want me too.
Take me in your arms.

REPEAT CHORUS

Your sensuous words drive me into a dream,

snippet.title: 'Twas the night before Apocalypse

localized.description:
'Twas the night before Apocalypse, when all through the house
I nervously paced and unbuttoned my blouse.
My stockings were pulled up each leg with much care,
And I'd teased, curled and sprayed every lock of my hair.

The girls were nestled all snug in their beds,
I'd had no carbohydrates- no rice and no breads.
But vodka doesn't count, so I poured a nightcap.
Probably had a bit much 'cause it dropped in my lap.

When out in the street there arose such a clatter,
That I reached for the door- Hey, I swear I look fatter!
Oh well, such is life.  So I gave one last flash,
Then forgot I had promised to take out the trash.

It's freaking L.A. Why's it feel like there's snow?
I could put on a jacket, but my outfit would blow.
When, what to my nearsighted eyes should appear?
It must be an asteroid!  Apocalypse is here!

I have many regrets, better do something quick!
I'll text my ex-boyfriend and call him a-
There's that one Christmas party where nobody came,
And that small structure fire caused by one tiny flame.

Well if this is the end, at least I look like a vixen.
I had a great life and I sure got my kicks in.
I'll set down my burdens and I'll sit on this wall,
And enjoy my last moments as the world starts to fall.

The $%*#?!  Nothing happened.  That's not how this works!
Those freaking Mayans, what a bunch of jerks!
I got myself dressed up and powdered my nose,
Then stood in the cold and I basically froze.

I'll head back inside. Did someone just whistle?
It looks like he's holding a toe made of mistle.
I should really get contacts, I have such poor sight.
Holy crap, it's Santa!  Gonna be a gooooooood night!

I love ewe guys!!!!

THANK YOU:
Nathan Moore

snippet.title: In Your Arms (Original)

localized.description:
IN YOUR ARMS

Lying here without you in the dark
Unable to breathe when you're so far
Yet the very thought of you brings solace to my heart

Can't believe we've held on for so long
Never knew that love could be so strong
Binding us together when we're near or we're apart
'Cause you saw right through me from the start

Hold me in your arms
Every time you leave
Every part of me longs for you to
Hold me in your arms
Missing you like crazy
Counting down the days 'till I see you again

Watching other couples holding hands
Knowing half of them don't stand a chance
Constantly reminded that the world can be unkind

Everyone said there would be a price
Though I never asked for their advice
Still they tried to warn that "out of sight" meant "out of mind"
Now it's clear that all of them are blind

Hold me in your arms
Ever since I kissed you
Everything is blissful to me when you
Hold me in your arms
Sends my heart racing
Thinking of the ways that you changed my life

And on the day we come together
I'll be the one embracing you

Hold me in your arms
Every time you leave
Every part of me longs for you to
Hold me in your arms
Missing you like crazy
Counting down the days 'till I see you again


Words & Music by Lana McKissack and Chester See

snippet.title: THE PASSING - A Horror Short Film

Lights Down. Volume up.
